{"tid":2308041,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"最強大叔團！Rain × 朴軫永有望明年元旦發片","createTime":"2020-12-01T14:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T15:09:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b79b67b5238d0ddb586613fb1548c9f105f04e8c","tid":2308041,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_d95398cf4575460457d67bb9194c97b3/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-01/132020-887141.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_d95398cf4575460457d67bb9194c97b3%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-01%2F132020-887141.png&h=b97c14be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRain 在 10 月底時就預告將和朴軫永組成雙人團體，隨著兩人一起在 YouTube 節目中露面，他們的「出道」消息也越來越讓人等不及啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今天（1 日）有媒體報導指 Rain 和朴軫永預定於 2021 年 1 月 1 日發行新歌音源，正式以雙人組之姿出道。不僅如此，還預告兩將在當天登上 KBS 1TV 的晨間節目《晨間庭院》。<br />\n<br />\n不過，Rain 的經紀公司 Rain Company 對此表示：「目前還在協調回歸行程，也在配合行程安排活動計畫。」對所有資訊仍十分保密。<br />\n<br />\n雖然關於雙人組的消息還不明朗，不過最近朴軫永已登上了 Rain 的 YouTube 節目《Season B Season》。看著兩人平時的有趣互動，真的很期待他們上台後的默契啊！"},{"pid":"2fe6415b77573efa0275e44aaedef769f7089deb","tid":2308041,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"g持daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ng持牙雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32534f082a69ba6773b2b71bea42b291622bef25","tid":2308041,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:45:27.000Z","msg":"支持！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096f5a5324fe7d658a7a9a76ebbc5cee8e10b117","tid":2308041,"uid":16659,"like":0,